text: Mikel Johnson (born 18 July 1987 ) is a German singer. == US5 == Mikel starred at TV show Big in America for US5. In 2007, after the release of "Rhythm Of Life", he persuaded his solo career and replaced by Vince Tomas. Category:German singers Category:1987 births Category:Living people
title: Mikel Johnson (singer, born 1987)
